{"article":{"id":900006616363,"url":"https://mackerelio.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/900006616363.json","html_url":"https://support.mackerel.io/hc/en-us/articles/900006616363-Is-it-possible-to-use-more-than-the-plan-s-limit-","author_id":390085917472,"comments_disabled":true,"draft":false,"promoted":false,"position":0,"vote_sum":0,"vote_count":0,"section_id":360008016131,"created_at":"2021-04-13T07:00:17Z","updated_at":"2021-09-06T01:29:26Z","name":"Is it possible to use more than the plan’s limit?","title":"Is it possible to use more than the plan’s limit?","source_locale":"ja","locale":"en-us","outdated":false,"outdated_locales":[],"edited_at":"2021-05-11T09:13:09Z","user_segment_id":null,"permission_group_id":1305651,"content_tag_ids":[],"label_names":[],"body":"\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eEach plan (Standard / Free / Trial) has its own limit on the number of items that can be used.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eThe specified limits for the Free plan and Trial plan cannot be exceeded.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eWith the Standard plan, if you exceed the limit of any of the following items, the overage is converted into standard hosts and additional fees are incurred.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eHost metrics\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eService metrics\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eExternal monitoring\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eAnomaly detection for roles\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eTo learn more about additional fees, see \"\u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://support.mackerel.io/hc/en-us/articles/360040109431\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eHandling of host conversion when plan limits are exceeded\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003e\".\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003e  By default, the following items cannot be exceeded, but you can request for these limits to be mitigated at no additional charge by contacting Support.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eMonitors\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eCustom dashboards\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eAs limit mitigation may take 1 to 2 business days, please let us know in advance.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eIn addition, please understand that we may decline a request depending on the situation.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c/p\u003e"}}